The paper focuses on facial attribute classification using deep neural networks, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves transfer learning and multi-label learning, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of unsupervised domain adaptation, which is a technique commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
